            <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Read Anaïs’ letter to her pen pal, Assia. The activities she mentions are missing and replaced by images. Based on those images, write the missing activities, using the word bank. Be sure to use the correct form of each verb.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style="border: 1px solid black; display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 99%;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;jouer aux cartes &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; aller à un festival de danse &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; bavarder &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; jouer aux échecs &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;envoyer des SMS&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ma chère Assia, &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Oui, j’aime 1. &lt;img style="border: 2px solid black; margin-top: 12px;" src="https://cdn.waysidepublishing.com/textbooks/QTI/ECF1/ecf1_u5_vgq_vq2_activity2_q1.jpg" alt="hand texting on cell phone" width="30%"&gt; mais je préfère 2. &lt;img style="border: 2px solid black; margin-top: 12px;" src="https://cdn.waysidepublishing.com/textbooks/QTI/ECF1/ecf1_u5_vgq_vq2_activity2_q2.jpg" alt="a girl having close conversation with another girl" width="30%"&gt; avec mon amie. En famille, nous 3. &lt;img style="border: 2px solid black; margin-top: 12px;" src="https://cdn.waysidepublishing.com/textbooks/QTI/ECF1/ecf1_u5_vgq_vq2_activity2_q3.jpg" alt="group of three friends around a table with playing cards laid out" width="30%"&gt;&amp;nbsp;. Maman 4. &lt;img style="border: 2px solid black; margin-top: 12px;" src="https://cdn.waysidepublishing.com/textbooks/QTI/ECF1/ecf1_u5_vgq_vq2_activity2_q4.jpg" alt="woman moving chess pieces on a board" width="30%"&gt; avec ses amies tous les vendredis. Ce weekend, mes frères 5. &lt;img style="border: 2px solid black; margin-top: 12px;" src="https://cdn.waysidepublishing.com/textbooks/QTI/ECF1/ecf1_u5_vgq_vq2_activity2_q5.jpg" alt="a stage with people doing break dance moves as audience watches" width="30%"&gt; . Et toi, qu’est-ce que tu fais ce weekend ?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1. [RESPONSE]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2. [RESPONSE1]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3. [RESPONSE2]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4. [RESPONSE3]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5. [RESPONSE4]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</mattext>
